{
  "stem": "23278.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was also the year of the occupation of the Saar, when they reoccupied the Rhineland and we didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was the year of the war in-- the Civil War in Spain, where we had refugees coming from all the bombings, you know, of all-- you know Picasso and all the shooting, Guernica and all.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at the same time, we had a lot of strikes in France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "France was a mess.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was when we had Leon Blum as president, and he was the one who-- who arranged and managed to have, for the French workers, the first time ever in history, vacation.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The French worker never had a day of vacation-- paid vacation-- ever, ever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it is Leon Blum who did that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it created a lot of problems.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was very enthusiastic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So was I.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But all the snobs said, here are they coming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We cannot go on vacation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All the Slavs are coming, messing up our vacation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, the usual, as you have that here with the blacks and-- OK.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was the time when we went to Germany and my father enrolled me in a school, not long, couple months in the Rhineland.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on top of the door of the school was written, in beautiful Gothic letter-- maybe you know German?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was written [GERMAN], which means, anybody who buys from the Jews is a traitor to his people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I went under that door and finally asked my dad, what does that mean?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he explained to me what the Jews were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I though the Jews were people in the Bible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I didn't know they existed now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I-- And you were 13 then?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was 13.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
